title: The Next Food Network Star S08E07 Meet the Press-ure x264
description:
Being a Food Network Star requires handling yourself with ease in the glare of the media spotlight.

Finalists will be more exposed than ever as they film their own promotional video -- without the support of their producers!

A panel of journalists grills each of the finalists with tough questions about their techniques, personal background and the show they want to bring to Food Network. Who can handle the journalists and who cracks under the pressure?
